long, parallelsided at base with rounded transparent lobes for apical 
<quantity box="[216,302,1203,1224]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="222" unit="mm" value="0.2">0.20 mm</quantity>
of parameres.
